 Toke Makinwa has opened up on her social media how her past trauma affected her love life. The star made it known that her past trauma made her difficult to love. The entrepreneur had earlier opened up about her struggle with Post Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD) and how therapy saved her. READ ALSO: Toke Makinwa Laments Poor Working Conditions Of Lagos Airport Workers Toke made this known through her Instagram on Sunday February 27 as she thanked God for not giving up on her.